<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error - Admin Dashboard</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700&family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
        }
        .brand-heading {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="max-w-md w-full text-center">
        <div class="mb-8 inline-block">
            <svg class="w-24 h-24 text-[#6C7559] mx-auto" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" 
                    d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z">
                </path>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <h1 class="brand-heading text-4xl font-bold text-[#6C7559] mb-4">Oops!</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-8">Something went wrong on our end.</p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
            <button onclick="window.location.href='/admin/dashboard'" 
                    class="w-full md:w-auto px-8 py-3 bg-[#6C7559] text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-[#5a6349] transition-colors duration-200">
                Return to Dashboard
            </button>
            
            <div class="flex justify-center">
                <button onclick="window.location.href='/admin/login'" 
                        class="text-[#6C7559] hover:text-[#5a6349] font-medium">
                    Return to Login
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 text-sm text-gray-500">
            <p>If this problem persists, please contact the system administrator.</p>
            <p class="mt-2">Error Code: <%= Date.now().toString(36) %></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#6C7559] to-[#A4B494]"></div>
<div class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#A4B494] to-[#6C7559]"></div>

</body>
</html>
